The '''Heorem Skytunnel''' was a kilometer-long tunnel that led through the [[Heorem Complex]] in the [[Senate District/Legends|Senate District]] on [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]. It provided transit for both [[Hovertrain/Legends|mag-levs]] and sky traffic, leading from the Senate District to [[Sah'c Canyon]] in the [[Quadrant H-46|Sah'c District]].

